    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "he's really resistant to going to the hospital and is worried about the cost and the whole ordeal if it's nothing. if we do the magnesium and salt thing, how much magnesium should he actually take to make sure it works? also, if the tingling goes away completely in the next few minutes, can we just call it a day and maybe check in with a doctor tomorrow instead?",
