      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For the magnesium, a standard dose of 400mg of magnesium citrate mixed into a large glass of water should help restore balance. If the tingling vanishes completely in the next few minutes, it is *still* not a guarantee that everything is fine, so do not dismiss it. However, if the symptoms are gone, a follow-up appointment the next day is acceptable, but keep an eye on him constantly for any return of weakness or slurring.",
